{"tid":2510711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］支持國家連登仔討論會 正式成立！","createTime":"2021-04-30T10:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T16:26:39.000Z","uid":84037,"like":20,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e5fab9299accc23b6c409567e90d2403a870e8b9","tid":2510711,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:46:27.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><p class=\"center\">🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳</p></span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><p class=\"center\">支持國家連登仔討論會 <br />\n簡稱支連會 <br />\n正式成立！</p></span></span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><p class=\"center\">🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳</p></span><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"maroon\">呢個討論串，係俾愛國家，愛香港嘅連登巴絲參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不愛國者歡迎挑機，我哋一定恥笑到你面都黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span></p><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"teal\"><span class=\"large\">討論守則<br />\n1. 暢所欲言，基本法保障咗言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 唔好同YC一般見識，鬧吓同笑吓佢哋就得，唔洗糾纏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 守望相助，見到有會友提出問題儘量解答，有咩就儘量幫，我哋都係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"e78ff1d92655b22c2f427570ce1ca690f0573d58","tid":2510711,"uid":66087,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:48:29.000Z","msg":"咩嘢支連會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c354d8b626111448bd2eb4df6ef96471358711","tid":2510711,"uid":254716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets